Lolla Venkata Revanth Kumar Sharma (born 10 February 1990) is an Indian playback singer, 
known for his songs in Telugu language. 
He also won Rock Star, Spicy Singer on Maa TV (now Star Maa) and Superstar of the South. 
He has sung around 200 songs for Telugu and Kannada films. He was the winner of Indian Idol Season 9. 
For the song "Manohari", from the film Baahubali: The Beginning, he received IIFA Utsavam and Star Maa Music Award nominations for best male playback singer
